{"tid":1706636,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方否認高層下令前線可胡亂開槍","createTime":"2019-11-11T06:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T06:37:13.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c418ad1326d1525c8fb0dcffc53c1735fb38585d","tid":1706636,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:37:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2712104922185991/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2712104922185991%2F&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddf4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=644e6824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2712104922185991/</a><br />\n<br />\n【警方否認高層下令前線可胡亂開槍】<br />\n<br />\n警方今午（11月11日）發聲明，承認有警務人員在西灣河曾開槍及射中一名男子；而在沙田及東涌的執法行動中，有警務人員曾拔出配槍及擎槍。<br />\n<br />\n對於網上有指控警隊高層下令前線人員今日行動中可胡亂開槍，警方嚴正澄清絕無此事，警隊強調對警務人員使用槍械有嚴格指引，所有警察都必須為自己的執法及行為負責。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-11-2019/57418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F11-11-2019%2F57418&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddf4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=2467ae1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-11-2019/57418</a><br />\n<br />\n#開槍 #西灣河<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddf4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=9ba6a95b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddf4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=b96d1852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=ra